[I] 3D space simulation

[T] Celestia is an OpenGL-based 3D space simulation for Unix and Win32 that
[T] lets you travel through the solar system, to the stars, and even beyond
[T] the galaxy. Visit over 100,000 stars, 100 solar system bodies, and all
[T] known extrasolar planets.

[U] https://celestiaproject.space/

[A] Chris Laurel
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/graphic

[L] GPL
[V] 1.7.0 cf0af26

